data.value:
Dear [PATIENT],

This is a friendly reminder of your upcoming Telehealth appointment with your provider at Cancer Treatment Centers of America© (CTCA).



Your appointment will be virtual, meaning you will connect with your provider through Microsoft Teams for a virtual interaction. Please ensure that your volume and microphone are turned on and your camera is facing you at the time of the appointment.


Please see the attached “How-To Guide” for instructions on joining your virtual appointment.


For CTCA Telehealth technical related questions please call 800-234-0577 or email CTCATelehealthSupport@ctca-hope.com with your full name, contact phone number and best time to reach you 7am-6pm CT.

[DATETIME]

Click the button 10-15 minutes before your appointment.

Join Meeting

Trouble Joining?

AUDIO INFORMATION

Phone: [PHONE]

Meeting ID: [MEETING ID]

data.name: ReadinessCheckEmailv2
data.value:
Hello [PATIENT],
In advance of your upcoming Telehealth Video Appointment with Cancer Treatment Centers of America® (CTCA), you’ll receive a call from our Technology Support Team. This call is simply to test your connectivity; it is not a medical appointment.
Tech Support Phone Call
[DATETIME]
Call will be within an hour of this scheduled start time.
If you need to reschedule this technology check, please call us at 1-800-234-0577.
Below is your test button— do not click this until you are on the phone with one of our technicians . Then you will be prompted to click.
Only click this when prompted to test
Please save this email as it contains information required to test your connectivity with CTCA® Tech Support.
To reschedule or cancel your readiness check, please call the scheduling team.
If using an Apple device, make sure you have iOS v15.2.0 or later. Download the latest update prior to your appointment.
Questions about technical issues related to your Telehealth Video appointment? Call 1-800-234-0577 or email CTCATelehealthSupport@ctca-hope.com with your full name, contact number and best time to reach you between 7 a.m.-6 p.m. CT.
© 2022 COH HoldCo Inc.
